    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "one cause of this issue is we don't have a lot of peers right now.\r\n\r\ndiscv5 sends a lot of peers to libp2p but it's all known peers to libp2p (initially libp2p load from db to its known peers list) so it does not dial and then not emit `peer:connect` event.\r\n\r\none workaround for the issue right now is to remove `.medalla/peerstore` before start/restart.\r\n",
